Package io.sentry.protocol

Class SdkInfo

java.lang.Object
io.sentry.protocol.SdkInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
JsonSerializable, JsonUnknown
public final class SdkInfo extends Object implements JsonUnknown, JsonSerializable
Holds information about the system SDK.

This is relevant for iOS and other platforms that have a system SDK. Not to be confused with the client SDK.
